To install PostgreSQL:

$ brew install postgresql
  or
$ brew upgrade postgresql


To install PostGIS:

$ brew install postgis --enable-ruby


To initialize DB, add the following to /etc/sysctl.conf:
kern.sysv.shmmax=4194304
kern.sysv.shmmin=1
kern.sysv.shmmni=32
kern.sysv.shmseg=8
kern.sysv.shmall=1024

Reboot, then call:

$ initdb /usr/local/var/postgres


To create a user:

$ createlang plpgsql <username_from_database.yml>
$ createuser <username_from_database.yml>

Be sure to make them a super-user

To install GSL:

$ brew install gsl

To setup the database:

$ rake db:create:all db:reset


To run the tests:

$ rake
